ref=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/smita-crishna-godrej\/#Career\" title=\"Career\">Career<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/smita-crishna-godrej\/#Awards\" title=\"Awards\">Awards<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/smita-crishna-godrej\/#Net_Worth\" title=\"Net Worth\">Net Worth<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/smita-crishna-godrej\/#FactsTrivia\" title=\"Facts\/Trivia\">Facts\/Trivia<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"WikiBiography\"><\/span>Wiki\/Biography<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<p>Smita Crishna Godrej was born in 1950 (<strong>age 73 years; as of 2023<\/strong>). She did her schooling at J B Petit School in Mumbai. She then went on to pursue BA in History and Political Science from St. Xavier&#8217;s College Mumbai.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Physical_Appearance\"><\/span>Physical Appearance<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>Height (approx.):<\/strong> 5&#8242; 6&#8243;<\/p>\n<p><strong>Weight (approx.):<\/strong> 55 kg<\/p>\n<p><strong>Hair Colour: <\/strong>Light Brown<\/p>\n<p><strong>Eye Colour: <\/strong>Dark Brown<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Smita-Crishna-Standing-scaled.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-185895\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Smita-Crishna-Standing-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"Smita Crishna Standing\" width=\"259\" height=\"895\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Smita-Crishna-Standing-scaled.jpg 741w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Smita-Crishna-Standing-87x300.jpg 87w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Smita-Crishna-Standing-296x1024.jpg 296w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Smita-Crishna-Standing-768x2652.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Smita-Crishna-Standing-445x1536.jpg 445w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Smita-Crishna-Standing-593x2048.jpg 593w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 259px) 100vw, 259px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Family\"><\/span>Family<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Smita belongs to the Godrej family, which established the Godrej group, a multinational conglomerate.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_185897\" style=\"width: 658px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/The-Godrej-family-tree.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-185897\" class=\" wp-image-185897\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/The-Godrej-family-tree.jpg\" alt=\"The Godrej family tree\" width=\"648\" height=\"393\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/The-Godrej-family-tree.jpg 800w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/The-Godrej-family-tree-300x182.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/The-Godrej-family-tree-768x466.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 648px) 100vw, 648px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-185897\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">The Godrej family tree<\/p><\/div>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Parents_Siblings\"><\/span><strong>Parents &amp; Siblings<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Smita Crishna&#8217;s father is Naval Godrej, co-founder of the Godrej group and her mother is Soonuben Godrej. She has a brother named Jamshyd Godrej who is engaged in the family business.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_185899\" style=\"width: 368px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Smitas-father-Naval-Godrej.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-185899\" class=\" wp-image-185899\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Smitas-father-Naval-Godrej.jpg\" alt=\"Smita's father Naval Godrej\" width=\"358\" height=\"436\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Smitas-father-Naval-Godrej.jpg 800w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Smitas-father-Naval-Godrej-247x300.jpg 247w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Smitas-father-Naval-Godrej-768x934.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 358px) 100vw, 358px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-185899\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Smita&#8217;s father Naval Godrej<\/p><\/div>\n<div id=\"attachment_185900\" style=\"width: 364px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Smitas-Brother-Jamshyd-Godrej.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-185900\" class=\" wp-image-185900\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Smitas-Brother-Jamshyd-Godrej.jpg\" alt=\"Smita's Brother Jamshyd Godrej\" width=\"354\" height=\"455\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Smitas-Brother-Jamshyd-Godrej.jpg 800w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Smitas-Brother-Jamshyd-Godrej-233x300.jpg 233w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Smitas-Brother-Jamshyd-Godrej-797x1024.jpg 797w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Smitas-Brother-Jamshyd-Godrej-768x987.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 354px) 100vw, 354px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-185900\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Smita&#8217;s Brother Jamshyd Godrej<\/p><\/div>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Husband_Children\"><\/span><strong>Husband &amp; Children<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Smita is married to Vijay Crishna, who is a well-known theatre actor. The couple has a daughter named Nyrika Holkar, who works with the Godrej group, and a son, Freyan.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_185902\" style=\"width: 445px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Smitas-husband-Vijay-Crishna.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-185902\" class=\" wp-image-185902\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Smitas-husband-Vijay-Crishna.jpg\" alt=\"Smita's husband Vijay Crishna\" width=\"435\" height=\"326\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Smitas-husband-Vijay-Crishna.jpg 800w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Smitas-husband-Vijay-Crishna-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Smitas-husband-Vijay-Crishna-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 435px) 100vw, 435px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-185902\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Smita&#8217;s husband Vijay Crishna<\/p><\/div>\n<div id=\"attachment_185904\" style=\"width: 448px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Smitas-daughter.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-185904\" class=\" wp-image-185904\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Smitas-daughter.jpg\" alt=\"Smita's daughter Nyrika Holkar\" width=\"438\" height=\"332\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Smitas-daughter.jpg 800w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Smitas-daughter-300x227.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Smitas-daughter-768x582.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 438px) 100vw, 438px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-185904\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Smita&#8217;s daughter Nyrika Holkar<\/p><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Career\"><\/span>Career<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Smita Crishna Godrej began her career by engaging herself in her family business, the Godrej group, a multinational conglomerate.\u00a0 Her brother Jamshyd Godrej is the managing director at Godrej &amp; Boyce. She holds a 20% stake in her company and is considered to be the third richest woman in India. The Godrej family owns the $6 billion revenue in Godrej Group, a 125-year-old consumer products giant.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Awards\"><\/span>Awards<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>In 2016, Smita Crishna-Godrej was awarded the Extraordinary Leadership Award by Education World at their Education World Grand Jury Awards 2016.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Net_Worth\"><\/span>Net Worth<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>She holds a net worth of $2.8 billion.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"FactsTrivia\"><\/span>Facts\/Trivia<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<ul>\n<li>Smita Crishna paid Rs 372 crore to buy Mehrangir, a house originally owned by nuclear researcher Homi Bhabha.\n<p><div id=\"attachment_185908\" style=\"width: 465px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Historic-Bungalow-Homi-Bhabha.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-185908\" class=\"wp-image-185908\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Historic-Bungalow-Homi-Bhabha.jpg\" alt=\"Historic Bungalow, Mehrangir\" width=\"455\" height=\"621\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Historic-Bungalow-Homi-Bhabha.jpg 800w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Historic-Bungalow-Homi-Bhabha-220x300.jpg 220w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Historic-Bungalow-Homi-Bhabha-750x1024.jpg 750w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Historic-Bungalow-Homi-Bhabha-768x1048.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 455px) 100vw, 455px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-185908\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Historic Bungalow, Mehrangir<\/p><\/div><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"489bcfb86580b123547338c91db0eff2\" data-index=\"3\" style=\"float: none; margin:3px 0 3px 0; text-align:center;\">\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\"\r\n     style=\"display:block\"\r\n     data-ad-format=\"autorelaxed\"\r\n     data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6769524711517462\"\r\n     data-ad-slot=\"2473600074\"><\/ins>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size: 0px; height: 0px; line-height: 0px; margin: 0; padding: 0; clear: both;\"><\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Smita Crishna Godrej is an Indian woman who holds a 20% stake in the Godrej empire and is known to be the third richest woman in India. Wiki\/Biography Smita Crishna Godrej was born in 1950 (age 73 years; as of 2023). She did her schooling at J B Petit School in Mumbai. She then went on to pursue BA in History and Political Science from St. Xavier&#8217;s College Mumbai. Physical Appearance Height (approx.): 5&#8242; 6&#8243; Weight (approx.): 55 kg Hair Colour: Light Brown Eye Colour: Dark Brown Family Smita belongs to the Godrej family, which established the Godrej group, a <\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":67,"featured_media":185890,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[19],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/185691"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/67"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=185691"}],"version-history":[{"count":9,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/185691\/revisi